{
  "stem": "11296.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going-- there's too many of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're going there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they took-- they took, I think, 2,000 women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They was most of them from-- from Auschwitz or from us, all the girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to a new place they called, Neustadt-Glewe, near-- Neustadt-Glewe not far from Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- so there we stayed, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went there and there was a very small-- a very small place, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This place consisted, you know, a few barracks, a few barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No work.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was-- I mean, there was a factory that was making-- that was making the-- the wings for the airplanes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then in this-- all the-- all the fliers had little houses in the woods there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there, you know, afterwards, when we got liberated-- this was a very short story because we stayed just there maybe three, four weeks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was already May.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you know, they start running away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the Germans left us alone in the-- in the the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was nothing, you know, nothing exciting going on there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody was looking just how to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Who died, died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was no-- no hospitals, no doctors, no crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Who died was buried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took all the people, you know, who died there was, I think, in the woods or someplace, made a big hole and put them in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians was very good to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They brought us, you know, what-- trucks with food and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told us to go to town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe five miles from the-- from the camp-- from this little camp there was a-- a-- it was a-- a beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not a one house was bombed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Beautiful place.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said, go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
